# thunderchief3000@yahoo.com
IMAPAccount yahoo-thunderchief3000
Host imap.mail.yahoo.com
User thunderchief3000@yahoo.com
PassCmd "oauth2 --feed thunderchief3000"
Port 993
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore yahoo-thunderchief3000-remote
Account yahoo-thunderchief3000

MaildirStore yahoo-thunderchief3000-local
Path  ~/Mail/thunderchief3000@yahoo.com/
Inbox ~/Mail/thunderchief3000@yahoo.com/Inbox

Channel yahoo-thunderchief3000
Master :yahoo-thunderchief3000-remote:
Slave :yahoo-thunderchief3000-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *

